Title: Robowars Competition Overview

Introduction
Robowars is a robotics combat competition where participants design and build remote-controlled robots to fight in an arena.

Objectives
The goal is to disable or immobilize the opponent robot using mechanical, electrical, or control-based strategies.

Rules
- Weight limits
- Weapon restrictions
- Safety requirements

Events
Robowars is conducted at technical festivals such as IIT Techfests and Techkriti.
